casebody.data:
No. 11A691. John Kasich, Governor of Ohio, et al., Applicants v. Charles Lorraine. 565 U.S. 1186, 132 S. Ct. 1306, 2012 U.S. LEXIS 1065.

181 L. Ed. 2d 1034,

February 8, 2012.

Application to vacate the stay of execution of sentence of death entered by the United States District Court for the Southern District of Ohio on January 11, 2012, presented to Justice Kagan, and by her referred to the Court, denied.

Same case below, 840 F. Supp. 2d 1044.
